welcome_message_body: Welcome to Warwick, where small town charm meets big city adventures. Known for its stunning natural landscapes and rich history, we invite you to explore and discover all that Warwick has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Warwick Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Warwick Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
